PrecisAmendments to the PENSION BENEFITS STANDARDS REGULATIONS, 1985 which exempt certain pension plans and benefits from the application of this Act, more particularly, plans established or created by a provincial statute, plans in respect of certain provincial telephone companies, as well as pension benefit credits that exceed the maximum amount that may be transferred under the Income Tax Act from one plan to another or to an R.R.S.P.
